<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavarṣaṁbulu 1189 gunēṁṭi vibhavasaṁ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vatsara māgha ba 14 guruvāramunāṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti sa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mastapraśastisahitaṁbaina śrīmatu sōmayadēva<unclear>di</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vyaśrīpādapadmārādhaka sakalādhibhaktulapādōda<unclear>ka</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>prasādōpajīvulaina pagame(ṁ)ccugaṁḍa koṁppula prōli
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nayuṁḍu muppasāni doḍḍadēvara naganabōyu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁḍunuṁ dama tātalu goppamāḍeḍḍiki taṁḍri nārebō
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yinki talli kommasānkiṁ dama Annalu koṟnupupā<unclear>ṭi</unclear> Eṟa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>pōtināyuniki ḍoṁkkena mārnēniki dharmmārtta<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>gā bejavā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍa mallēśvaraśrīmahadēvaraku Akhaṁḍḍadīpamulu 2 ki I
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ccina mōdalu 50 vīni jēkoni nūnekommanalubōyuni (ko)
<lb n="12"/>ko sōmanabōyuṁḍu tana putranupau(vu)trikamu Āca
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁdrārkka<unclear>stā</unclear>yigā nitya Aḍḍeṁḍu ne<supplied reason="omitted">yi</supplied><unclear>pō</unclear>yaṁgalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> I bō
<lb n="14" break="no"/>yniki cilukapuṁḍini būmi kha 2 pēyēṭa bhūmi kha 1 dēvara
<lb n="15"/>nivēdyanakai nāgarapuṁ <unclear>bo</unclear>lāna bhūmi kha 1 Ā nāga<unclear>na</unclear>
<lb n="16" break="no"/>bōyuṁḍu sēIṁcina <unclear>kirī</unclear>ṭamu 1 dīniyettu naga 28 vanne
<lb n="17"/>15 vīri peṭina kaṁcu(ka)kaṁbamu 1 dīni yettu pa 1100 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="18"/>svadataṁ paradataṁ vā vyō
<lb n="19"/>harēti vasuṁdharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭiva
<lb n="20" break="no"/>rṣasahasraṇi viṣṭāyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> jā
<lb n="21" break="no"/>yatē krimi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
